overview:
# sciwasm

> SciPy-inspired scientific computing in TypeScript with WebAssembly acceleration.

## Modules

- Optimization (optimize)
- Integration (integrate)
- Interpolation (interpolate)
- Statistics (stats)
- Signal Processing (signal)
- Spatial (spatial)
- Special Functions (special)
- Sparse Matrices (sparse)
- Clustering (cluster)
- I/O (io)
- N-D Image Processing (ndimage)
- Constants (constants)
